<body>
   <div class="contain">
    <div class="top-section">
    <h1> How to became a Chartered Accountant after completing your class 10th</h1>
    <p>
        Register for the CA Foundation Course: The first step is to register for the CA Foundation course after completing 10+2 or its equivalent from a recognized board.

    </p>
    </div> 
     <div class="timeline">
        <div class="line"></div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Clear the CA Foundation Exam</h2>
                
                <p>
                    You need to clear the CA Foundation Exam to move to the next level of the CA course.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
              <h2> Register for CA Intermediate
                </h2>
                <p>
                    After clearing the CA Foundation Exam, you need to register for the CA Intermediate course.

                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Complete Articleship</h2>
                <p>
                    During the CA Intermediate course, you need to complete three years of articleship training under a practicing Chartered Accountant.



                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Get certified:
                </h2>
                <p>
                    While it is not mandatory to be certified to work as a chef, it can enhance your job prospects. You can consider getting certified by the American 
                    Culinary Federation (ACF) or other culinary associations.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>
                    Clear CA Intermediate Exam
                </h2>
                <p>
                    After completing the articleship training, you need to clear the CA Intermediate Exam to move to the next level of the CA course.



                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>
                    Register for CA Final
                </h2>
                <p>
                    After clearing the CA Intermediate Exam, you need to register for the final level of the CA course, i.e., CA Final.

                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>
                    Complete Articleship and Advanced Course
                </h2>
                <p>
                    During the CA Final course, you need to complete the remaining period of your articleship training and also complete an advanced course on information technology.

                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>
                    Clear CA Final Exam
                </h2>
                <p>
                    After completing the articleship and the advanced course, you need to clear the CA Final Exam.



                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>
                    Complete GMCS and ITT
                </h2>
                <p>
                    You need to complete the General Management and Communication Skills (GMCS) course and the Information Technology Training (ITT) course.




                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>
                    Obtain Membership
                </h2>
                <p>
                    After completing all the above steps and meeting all the criteria, you can apply for membership of the Institute of Chartered Accountants of India (ICAI) and become a Chartered Accountant.




                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
      
     </div>
   </div>
</body>
